{"tid":1235593,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"摧毀新興網上共媒，取消負責人外國護照及國籍（之前搞取消林家英國籍嘅巴打入）","createTime":"2019-06-17T07:32:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T12:43:45.000Z","uid":39752,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f44f9a0fe3dc6334c00e3981c01aeb9563794c54","tid":1235593,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:32:59.000Z","msg":"廢話唔講，我都唔撚知嗰啲開心大發現「幫港出聲造謠啊喂」嘅連登仔瞓撚咗幾耐<br />\n之前問大家周融係咪有英國籍又好似無人睇得明咁<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">俾條所有新興共媒嘅負責人清單大家</span></strong><br />\nSource：點、橙、輕、G、堅.... 建制網媒出沒注意！／Google／維基百科<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%BB%9E-%E6%A9%99-%E8%BC%95-g-%E5%A0%85-%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6%E7%B6%B2%E5%AA%92%E5%87%BA%E6%B2%92%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%25BB%259E-%25E6%25A9%2599-%25E8%25BC%2595-g-%25E5%25A0%2585-%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%2588%25B6%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E5%25AA%2592%25E5%2587%25BA%25E6%25B2%2592%25E6%25B3%25A8%25E6%2584%258F%2F&d=goC%2B%2BwCxwRgX8SEPTes0uyVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=1a9056d6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%25BB%259E-%25E6%25A9%2599-%25E8%25BC%2595-g-%25E5%25A0%2585-%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%2588%25B6%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E5%25AA%2592%25E5%2587%25BA%25E6%25B2%2592%25E6%25B3%25A8%25E6%2584%258F%2F&h=523de54a\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%BB%9E-%E6%A9%99-%E8%BC%95-g-%E5%A0%85-%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6%E7%B6%B2%E5%AA%92%E5%87%BA%E6%B2%92%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F/</a><br />\n<br />\n港人講地：齊心基金（<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">張震遠</span></strong>、<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">梁振英</span></strong>、<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">鄧爾邦</span></strong>、<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">馮煒光</span></strong>）<br />\nHKG 報：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">周融</span></strong>、<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">屈穎妍</span></strong><br />\n幫港出聲／「保普選反佔中」大聯盟：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">周融</span></strong><br />\n堅料網：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">陳崇煒</span></strong>（曾經冚旗又重開可能易手）<br />\n橙新聞：中聯辦（<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">符俊傑</span></strong>）<br />\n輕新聞：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">李炘</span></strong><br />\n點新聞：文匯報<br />\n<br />\n上面出現咗兩次嘅人名周融，旗下幫港出聲同埋香港G報係藍絲廢老一大消息源之一<br />\n因為呢條粉腸係做媒體出身，好清楚應該點做媒體，咁多年嚟已經有好多人落疊<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請大家幫手做三件事</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 列出所有呢一類造謠共媒，包括埋啲外圍 page 同 group，例如乜嘢看世界之類<br />\n2. 查出負責人及國籍<br />\n3. 如果有外國護照或國籍，由外國巴接力幫佢哋取消<br />\n一邊拎住外國籍一邊幫另一個國家抹黑香港，隨時代表佢有間諜行為，雖然無柒婆咁嚴重但都有得打</span></span><br />\n第四件事係大家自由發揮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>你哋咁撚鍾意奶共搞香港，留喺度做一世中國人啦，求之不得啦係咪先</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6d657c0cfe7805cad7784a605b993aae79ffedc","tid":1235593,"uid":39752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:37:23.000Z","msg":"係咪無人睇過自己老豆老母facebook一大堆幫港出聲啊，做嘢呀喂"},{"pid":"27bda183d0a77be91cc9249ea7628cafc577e6e8","tid":1235593,"uid":227769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:41:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"611575cd9610af99fbd929b83f4f575a0ae95896","tid":1235593,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:44:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cae7a0ea105f0ab44429d04648f0079c1fdc10dd","tid":1235593,"uid":39752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:51:47.000Z","msg":"唔做嘢就唔撚好問啲謠言邊度嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"973a91e85dd6de2c4d3e3dbcbd43035818167dd5","tid":1235593,"uid":100760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:54:08.000Z","msg":"pushhhhh"},{"pid":"537e7fe05d7f5d30cc2d5e8e8bd52486a7e5b619